### Imports compartilhados (todos os tracks)

```typescript
// API client
import { api } from '@/lib/api'

// Formatters
import { formatCpfCnpj, formatCurrency, formatDate } from '@/lib/formatters'

// Auth store
import { useAuthStore } from '@/stores/auth.store'

// Global hooks
import { useDebounce } from '@/hooks/use-debounce'
import { useNotification } from '@/hooks/use-notification'

// React Query
import { useQuery, useMutation, useQueryClient } from '@tanstack/react-query'

// React Hook Form + Zod (T3 apenas)
import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form'
import { zodResolver } from '@hookform/resolvers/zod'
import { z } from 'zod'

// Navigation
import { useRouter, useParams } from 'next/navigation'
import Link from 'next/link'
```

### Tokens de cor

```
Status SLA:
- Verde (ok):     text-success-base / bg-success-alpha-10
- Laranja (alerta): text-warning-base / bg-warning-alpha-10
- Vermelho (atrasado): text-error-base / bg-error-alpha-10

KPI Financeiro:
- Total:    text-text-strong-950 / bg-bg-white-0
- Pago:     text-success-base / bg-success-alpha-10
- Pendente: text-warning-base / bg-warning-alpha-10
- Vencido:  text-error-base / bg-error-alpha-10

Badges personType:
- PF: variant="neutral"
- PJ: variant="primary"
```

### Convencoes de arquivo

```
Componentes: kebab-case (client-form.tsx, activity-card.tsx)
Types: kebab-case (client.types.ts)
Hooks: use-{nome}.ts
Services: {feature}.service.ts
Schemas: {feature}.schema.ts
Pages: page.tsx (Next.js App Router)
```

